{category, ["code"]}.
{depends, ["mnesia","stdlib"]}.
{keywords, ["timer", "mnesia", "ordered_set"]}.
{summary, "Timer for large numbers of concurrent timers"}.
{abstract,"This application re-implements the standard timer module to "
 "work for very large numbers of concurrent timers. "
 "This implementation uses an mnesia ordered_set table to hold "
 "the timers, which is much more scaleable than the ordered list "
 "used in the standard timer module."}.
